oke she usually inhaled while her husband smoked until she had a preterm birth January 8, 2017 In "Health" ‘I’ll never forget the moment I was told my baby would die at birth,’ Sandra says. ‘I burst into tears. Andrew was devastated April 1, 2017 In "Just Human"